as soon as I entered,

00:06:06.240 --> 00:06:07.840
but it never crossed my mind.

00:06:09.430 --> 00:06:10.690
Don't blame yourself.

00:06:11.000 --> 00:06:13.170
Who would be wary of a young kid?

00:06:13.430 --> 00:06:14.260
Besides,

00:06:14.680 --> 00:06:16.230
